1) First always fork the GIT project to your workspace
2) Clone the forked GIT Project in to you Visual Studio Workspace
3) Add your Google API Key in to you .env properties file
4) Create a virtual conda python environment in the top space bar "> Create Python Environment"
5) Do pip install dotenv 
6) Do pip install of all python packages mentioned in requirments.txt file
7) To run the program use the command "streamlit run app.py" file (If your .py file is different name use that)
8) It will open the browser and you can fulfill all your functionalities
